OL,3,CCalls for paedophile Jeffrey Donaldson
OL,4,Cto be stripped of knighthood
OL,6,FThere have been calls to immediately
OL,7,Frevoke Jeffrey Donaldson's knighthood.
OL,9,FDonaldson was found guilty on Monday
OL,10,Fat Newry Crown Court of 18 historical
OL,11,Fsexual offences against two women when
OL,12,Fthey were children.
OL,14,FThe former Democratic Unionist Party
OL,15,Fleader, 63, was appointed to the Privy
OL,16,FCouncil in 2007 and was recognised by
OL,17,Fthe late Queen Elizabeth II in her
OL,18,F2016 Birthday Honours and given a
OL,19,Fknighthood.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
