PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1782404310
OL,3,CCalls for paedophile Jeffrey Donaldson
OL,4,Cto be stripped of knighthood
OL,6,FCurrent DUP leader Gavin Robinson was
OL,7,Famong senior unionists calling for
OL,8,FDonaldson's knighthood and membership
OL,9,Fof the Privy Council to be removed.
OL,11,FUlster Unionist leader Jon Burrows
OL,12,Falso said all state honours previously
OL,13,Fbestowed on Donaldson should be
OL,14,Fremoved "without delay".
OL,16,FHe said: "There is no rank, no title
OL,17,Fand no past office that places anyone
OL,18,Fabove the law.
OL,26,@vD@IOUvD@WO]xD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
