PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1782404310
OL,3,CCalls for paedophile Jeffrey Donaldson
OL,4,Cto be stripped of knighthood
OL,6,F"Jeffrey Donaldson abused his power
OL,7,Fand betrayed everyone who ever placed
OL,8,Ftheir faith in him.
OL,10,F"He must now be stripped of all state
OL,11,Fhonours without delay: no honour of
OL,12,Fthe state should remain in the hands
OL,13,Fof a man convicted of crimes of this
OL,14,Fnature.
OL,16,FTraditional Unionist Voice leader Jim
OL,17,FAllister said he had tabled a motion
OL,18,Fin the House of Commons which would
OL,19,Fcall on the Prime Minister to
OL,20,Frecommend to the King that Donaldson's
OL,21,Fknighthood be removed.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOU
