OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1782404310
OL,3,CCalls for paedophile Jeffrey Donaldson
OL,4,Cto be stripped of knighthood
OL,6,FHonours can be removed with the
OL,7,Fapproval of the King after the advice
OL,8,Fand consideration of the Forfeiture
OL,9,FCommittee, which is convened under the
OL,10,FCabinet Office.
OL,12,FAs honour recipients are expected to
OL,13,Fbe good citizens and role models,
OL,14,Fhonours can be removed from those
OL,15,Ffound guilty of criminal offences or
OL,16,Fthose who bring the honour system into
OL,17,Fdisrepute.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1782404310
OL,3,CCalls for paedophile Jeffrey Donaldson
OL,4,Cto be stripped of knighthood
OL,6,FThe committee will consider cases in
OL,7,Fthe wake of legal proceedings and
OL,8,Fanyone convicted for sexual offences
OL,9,Fwill automatically be considered for
OL,10,Fforfeiture.
OL,12,FThis process also applies for anyone
OL,13,Ffound to have committed a sexual act
OL,14,Ffollowing a trial of the facts.
OL,16,FThere is no time restriction on
OL,17,Foffences the committee will consider.
OL,19,FThe body's recommendations for
OL,20,Fforfeiture are submitted through the
OL,21,FPrime Minister to the King.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
