PN,41706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1782404310
OL,3,CCalls for paedophile Jeffrey Donaldson
OL,4,Cto be stripped of knighthood
OL,6,FIf the King gives his approval, a
OL,7,Fnotice of forfeiture is usually
OL,8,Fpublished on the Government website
OL,9,Fand placed in the London Gazette.
OL,11,FThe Cabinet office said those who have
OL,12,Ftheir honour removed are asked to
OL,13,Freturn their insignia to Buckingham
OL,14,FPalace and can no longer make any
OL,15,Freference to their having an honour in
OL,16,Fthe future.
OL,18,FThis would include use of the honour
OL,19,Fpost-nominals on websites,
OL,20,Fpublications or business cards.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/7
